On the contact page, we allow you to set a message. This message can also be edited. In this message you can give further information
to your users about how to use the contact form, or how quick they will get an answer to your request. We allow you to edit that 
message here, using an WYSIWYG editor ... This message will be used in the contact widget, right above the contact form to inform
your users of what they should do to properly contact you ...